snippets.title: DataMigrationService convertConversionWorkspace Sample

snippets.title: DataMigrationService commitConversionWorkspace Sample
snippets.description: Marks all the data in the conversion workspace as committed.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService rollbackConversionWorkspace Sample
snippets.description: Rolls back a conversion workspace to the last committed snapshot.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService applyConversionWorkspace Sample
snippets.description: Applies draft tree onto a specific destination database.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService describeDatabaseEntities Sample
snippets.description: Describes the database entities tree for a specific conversion workspace and a specific tree type. Database entities are not resources like conversion workspaces or mapping rules, and they can't be created, updated or deleted. Instead, they are simple data objects describing the structure of the client database.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService searchBackgroundJobs Sample
snippets.description: Searches/lists the background jobs for a specific conversion workspace. The background jobs are not resources like conversion workspaces or mapping rules, and they can't be created, updated or deleted. Instead, they are a way to expose the data plane jobs log.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService describeConversionWorkspaceRevisions Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves a list of committed revisions of a specific conversion workspace.

snippets.title: DataMigrationService fetchStaticIps Sample
snippets.description: Fetches a set of static IP addresses that need to be allowlisted by the customer when using the static-IP connectivity method.
